00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:55,720
I need to check

294
00:22:59,130 --> 00:23:00,810
You just have to poke at the sore spot don’t you

295
00:23:01,930 --> 00:23:03,360
But what am I supposed to do

296
00:23:03,980 --> 00:23:05,610
I don’t need you anymore anyway

297
00:23:13,890 --> 00:23:15,430
Yebin’s dead now

298
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:17,490
Only Kang Yebin is left

299
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:20,130
I’m gonna step over

300
00:23:21,030 --> 00:23:22,680
all the memories I had with you

301
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:24,590
and just move on

302
00:24:33,190 --> 00:24:34,200
Yebin unnie

303
00:24:34,930 --> 00:24:36,270
why did you come here

304
00:24:37,030 --> 00:24:38,760
Did the practice schedule change or something

305
00:24:39,730 --> 00:24:41,130
Just call me unnie

306
00:24:41,570 --> 00:24:42,980
It’s not an official schedule right now

307
00:24:48,290 --> 00:24:49,910
You’ve practiced a lot

308
00:24:52,530 --> 00:24:53,690
Drink some water first

309
00:24:58,850 --> 00:24:59,610
Thanks

310
00:25:30,490 --> 00:25:31,640
No that’s not true

311
00:25:33,340 --> 00:25:34,550
Fix your gestures first

312
00:25:35,050 --> 00:25:36,270
Why are you avoiding eye contact like that

313
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:54,210
Exactly

314
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,690
Stretch it out like this

315
00:25:58,780 --> 00:26:00,140
then open it up like that

316
00:26:03,290 --> 00:26:04,480
Starting from here

317
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:07,490
just like this

318
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:16,420
Don’t just watch with your eyes make it a habit with your body

319
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:18,760
Ah and

320
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:20,460
don’t get me wrong

321
00:26:21,230 --> 00:26:23,130
I’m not telling you this because of you

322
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:24,900
it’s for the sake of our team

323
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:26,670
Yes

324
00:26:28,490 --> 00:26:30,740
WONDERX is the group I built

325
00:26:33,290 --> 00:26:34,060
Yes

326
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:35,290
Do it again

327
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:57,860
Exactly

328
00:26:59,360 --> 00:27:00,250
You need to engage your core

329
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:01,890
through your waist

330
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:15,980
Close your eyes now

331
00:27:16,890 --> 00:27:18,260
and just listen to the beat

332
00:27:19,490 --> 00:27:20,860
Put strength into your core

333
00:27:22,690 --> 00:27:23,760
It's okay

334
00:27:24,120 --> 00:27:25,070
I'm here

335
00:27:25,530 --> 00:27:26,510
Just trust me

336
00:27:28,290 --> 00:27:29,630
If you close your eyes

337
00:27:30,790 --> 00:27:31,690
it might feel scary

338
00:27:34,250 --> 00:27:35,050
It’s okay

339
00:27:35,710 --> 00:27:37,790
When I say one, two, three, go around

340
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:42,090
One, two, three

341
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,020
Again

342
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:50,350
You need

343
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:52,240
to tense your core

344
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:54,630
Let's do it again

345
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:57,150
One, two, three

346
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:03,690
Your dancing’s slipped quite a bit

347
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,990
I’ve just been resting for a while

348
00:28:09,210 --> 00:28:10,880
It’s been a long time since we danced

349
00:28:11,660 --> 00:28:12,860
and I feel the same

350
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:22,040
There’s a group lesson next week

351
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:23,770
so make sure you’ve practiced everything by then

352
00:28:25,630 --> 00:28:27,920
The studio closes early today, so let’s wrap up quickly

353
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,860
You showed up right on time

354
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:19,600
You’re better at keeping your promises than three years ago

355
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:36,860
So, where should we start today

356
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:38,690
I’ll make a guess

357
00:29:39,690 --> 00:29:41,230
From beginning to end

358
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:42,730
You have to dance it all by yourself

359
00:29:43,210 --> 00:29:45,150
Once you’re on stage, no one can help you

360
00:29:48,930 --> 00:29:51,090
I’ll record it on my phone

361
00:29:51,460 --> 00:29:52,890
After you finish dancing

362
00:29:53,010 --> 00:29:55,370
You have to tell me yourself what you got wrong

363
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:57,690
You need to be able to do that

364
00:29:57,870 --> 00:30:00,140
That’s the minimum to earn the right to get on stage

365
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,230
Stop

366
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:28,590
You got the movement wrong here

367
00:30:28,720 --> 00:30:29,360
and

368
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,220
your gaze drifted

369
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:35,160
Your eyes kept slipping here

370
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,350
You got the choreography wrong

371
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:44,050
Why are you so scared

372
00:30:45,510 --> 00:30:46,130
Yeah

373
00:30:47,290 --> 00:30:49,330
You left me behind so easily three years ago

374
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,940
so what exactly are you afraid of now

375
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:56,360
What’s got you so sorry

376
00:30:57,970 --> 00:30:59,530
I didn’t come because of you Unnie

377
00:31:02,250 --> 00:31:03,820
I came for my debut spot

378
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,390
Alright

379
00:31:13,700 --> 00:31:15,470
Then keep practicing the chorus dance

380
00:31:16,460 --> 00:31:17,530
until you’re happy with it

381
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:52,090
So you’re both here

382
00:31:53,060 --> 00:31:54,230
That’s good news

383
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:57,770
Next week WONDERX’s new show is confirmed

384
00:31:58,420 --> 00:31:59,150
That’s where

385
00:31:59,430 --> 00:32:00,990
Jien will be officially introduced

386
00:32:02,890 --> 00:32:04,060
One week

387
00:32:04,430 --> 00:32:05,990
That seems too soon

388
00:32:11,770 --> 00:32:12,840
Still

389
00:32:16,390 --> 00:32:17,470
Is this being a bother

390
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:19,230
or is it shameful

391
00:32:24,850 --> 00:32:25,830
Still

392
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,960
there's a week left

393
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:31,360
I'll take care of it

394
00:32:32,660 --> 00:32:34,230
Make the schedule please

395
00:32:48,490 --> 00:32:50,060
Dance it again

396
00:33:04,690 --> 00:33:06,250
Keep dancing

397
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:23,460
Stop stop

398
00:33:24,430 --> 00:33:27,000
That's not dancing, it's a call for help

399
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:29,390
No

400
00:33:29,520 --> 00:33:30,790
The moves are hard right now

401
00:33:31,610 --> 00:33:33,180
Yeah they are hard but

402
00:33:33,610 --> 00:33:35,180
How can you be that cute about it

403
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,860
What

404
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,420
What do you mean by cute

405
00:33:40,030 --> 00:33:40,960
Cause it’s true

406
00:33:42,340 --> 00:33:42,980
Tch

407
00:33:48,290 --> 00:33:49,260
Try again

408
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:51,190
Okay I'll try once more

409
00:33:58,190 --> 00:33:58,940
Hey hey hey

410
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:02,710
If you keep dancing like that I'll have to carry you to the nurse's office

411
00:34:04,620 --> 00:34:05,720
You want me to carry you

412
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:07,590
I'm okay with that

413
00:34:08,790 --> 00:34:09,889
What’s that about

414
00:34:11,699 --> 00:34:13,139
Stop joking around

415
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:15,370
there’s a point to this move

416
00:34:15,659 --> 00:34:17,260
first, try controlling your breath

417
00:34:17,699 --> 00:34:18,370
like this

418
00:34:21,290 --> 00:34:21,960
Then

419
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:23,429
just

420
00:34:24,530 --> 00:34:25,190
turn like this

421
00:34:26,659 --> 00:34:28,030
That’s seriously cheating

422
00:34:29,090 --> 00:34:29,760
what do you mean

423
00:34:31,090 --> 00:34:32,290
You’re good at everything all by yourself

424
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:40,010
If you count one two, it starts spinning

425
00:34:41,030 --> 00:34:42,230
one two

426
00:34:42,929 --> 00:34:44,280
ticklish

427
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:45,929
Hey

428
00:34:46,630 --> 00:34:47,929
I don't have time for that now

429
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:52,429
Hey

430
00:34:52,889 --> 00:34:53,230
Yeah

431
00:34:58,460 --> 00:34:59,090
So how is it

432
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:02,690
She’s cute but kind

433
00:35:02,980 --> 00:35:03,710
of like a comedian

434
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,440
If we debut with this

435
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:08,860
let's perform it on the Aengkong stage

436
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:14,330
I really just want you to be happy

437
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:16,560
more than anything

438
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:19,560
Wait what’s that supposed to mean

439
00:35:21,650 --> 00:35:22,820
Ah it’s nothing

440
00:35:24,130 --> 00:35:24,630
Let's

441
00:35:25,130 --> 00:35:26,300
definitely debut together

442
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:51,650
Why are you crying

443
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:54,760
If you cry on stage

444
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:59,090
the fans in the crowd won’t even notice

445
00:36:01,030 --> 00:36:03,750
She’s always been that kind of hard worker

